        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You can use a use of your @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.3Dlq6orj97yca72n]{Wild Shape} ability to protect your allies.​</p><p><em>You conjure floating rocks to float around your allies and protect them. You selectively draw terrain and other obstacles, clearing a path at the same time.</em></p><p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - 6 Allies (30 ft) - 10 Minutes - Magical​</p><ul><li><p>They gain temporary hit points equal to [[/healing 5+(@classes.druid.level /2) temp]]{5 + half your druid level (rounded down)}.</p></li><li><p>While they have these temporary hit points, they have half cover.</p></li><li><p>You can use @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.HgIwBTZyXFaTVnX0]{Cragged Path} when you use Shield of the Crags without expending a use of @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.3Dlq6orj97yca72n]{Wild Shape}.</p></li></ul>",
